Now, if you're looking for the mage robe, it can drop off the Entolling Essence Channelers.  I haven't killed one yet, but I did get jumped by one during downtime... I was at like 80m and pet was at about 70 health... chain casted heals on pet and threw in a nuke or two when my pet landed a stun... however, I went oom and pet died, then I proceeded to get summoned by him and was lucky to get a gate off.  I do believe if I was FM and completely prepared, I would have won the battle, and might have gotten myself a robe (I will be trying again when I have time).  The flowers that someone mentioned earlier I know drop the Warrior BP, I didn't solo one, but a lvl 61 chanter friend and me duo'd it.<br>
As for me, I am nowhere near uber, I have decent gear I would say for being in a guild that just recently started doing Vindi, but you can check my stuff out by clicking my name below.  Also, one more thing, be aware that all these mobs are of certain classes, horses are generally druids, some things are enchanters.... may luck and a full mana bar be with you if you pull a horse that has been hasted and buffed by his friends  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
